1.name: wordpress/multisite-admin-bar-switcher
1.description:
The Multisite Admin Bar Switcher is a plugin written for WordPress Multi-Site that makes switching between sites easier with large numbers of sites.

This plugin replaces the built in 'sites' drop down with one which breaks the sites up by letter.
